{
  "stem": "17001.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, we never-- we never would-- would think that such a thing exists.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one time when the Blockalteste said, this is going to be Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do not fast because then you will faint and you will be taken to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on that particular day, on Yom Kippur, I was walking-- because I was always searching.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was always walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I stay near the barrack, I see only lice and-- and people who are dying and hunger and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figure, let me look around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I get something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as I was walking towards the end of the barrack-- because end of the [GERMAN] was the trains station-- I mean the train tracks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was the trains was coming in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this man at the other-- other side of the [GERMAN] there, we called that the Czech.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Czech lager.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we arrive to Auschwitz, there was a lot of Czech people, families together with their own clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were in that lager.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from one night to the next, they emptied the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But previous to that, I witnessed where one of the Blockalteste was doing business with one of the men from the Czech lager.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The man was throwing big heavy skiing shoes through the fence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them landed all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other one got caught in the fence, so she-- she couldn't get it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this Blockalteste was throwing bread over the fence to this guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had seen a small little blanket, a beautifully designed little blanket, that also this guy had thrown over the fence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So when I seen that, I said to myself that there is business going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
